      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Clean, good-condition vehicle that presents well overall and has clearly been cared for. The exterior and interior are in solid shape for its age, with normal wear and a few minor cosmetic imperfections you\u2019d expect from regular use, but nothing that takes away from it as a dependable, well-kept car. It offers a strong balance of condition and value for someone looking for a nice driver without paying mint-condition money.",
