    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "$4,200 - Inexpensive entry point for someone looking for a running, usable car they can tinker with or improve over time. This is a rough, poor-condition example with visible cosmetic wear, an overall tired appearance, and the kind of age-related needs you\u2019d expect at this price point. That said, it still has value as honest budget transportation or a project for a buyer who wants something affordable and straightforward.",
