    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Outstanding mint-condition example that should appeal strongly to buyers looking for a top-tier, exceptionally well-kept vehicle. It presents beautifully inside and out, with an exterior that shows very little to no noticeable wear and an interior that appears remarkably clean, fresh, and carefully preserved. This is the kind of vehicle that stands out for how well it has been maintained and how little it appears to have been used relative to most examples on the market. Buyers can expect a highly attractive, turn-key car that needs nothing cosmetically and should satisfy even picky shoppers seeking one of the nicest examples available.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and straightforward, this vehicle offers an affordable way to get on the road without stretching your wallet. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values function, flexibility, and price-conscious ownership. A sensible option for local driving, a work commuter, or a starter vehicle, with clear value for someone looking for basic transportation at an accessible price.",
      "price": 4950.0,
