      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels or a solid project to tinker with? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it still has plenty to offer for the right buyer. A great option if you need inexpensive transportation, a learner car, or something to work on in your spare time. Honest value here at a price that leaves room for improvements\u2014come take a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a strong-running engine, dependable transmission operation, and a chassis that still feels honest on the road. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it has the kind of straightforward mechanical character enthusiasts appreciate\u2014responsive throttle, usable torque, and the sort of platform that rewards a little TLC. A practical option for someone who wants affordable transportation, a shop runabout, or a hands-on weekend revival. Priced to move and well worth a look for buyers who value mechanical potential over showroom presentation.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
